					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">First, given two rectangles specified by left, right, top, and bottom, determine whether they overlap. Can you do that?
<br />
<br />Then for each game object, construct its bounding box. (Normally, games will leave a few pixels outside the bounding box to compensate for the fact that sprite cels aren't rectangular.)
<br />
<br />For each pair of game objects, compare their bounding boxes to see if they overlap.</div>

